Klokɛnspili kɛna cɩmʊ wonuu ŋgʊ pamakɩna nɛ ñɩɩtʊ ɖaŋ yɔ. Pama-kʊ ɛlɛ kiselu nɛ wiliu nakʊyʊ lɩʊ nɛ kɩ-taa. Pierre-Joseph Leblan lubina-kʊ pɩnaɣ 1763 taa. Klokɛnspili wɛ ndɩ nɛ kpandɩ kolokolo. Kpandɩ kolokolo ɛlɛ palaba-kʊ nɛ kpoŋgbolonaa. Pamakɩ klokɛnspili ɛlɛ, pamakɩ-kʊ ɛlɛ wiliu kʊɖʊmʊ kɛkɩlʊ lɩzʊ nɛ kiwiu kɩkɩlʊ kpandɩ kolokolo. Yee maɖʊ ɛsɔɔla se witu ɛlɛɛzɩ camɩyɛ kɔyɔ, ɛpɩzʊ ɛmabɩna kpoŋgbolo yaa paanɛ ñɩɩtʊ kɔyɔ, pɩwɛna-ɩ se esiduu camɩyɛ. 

Papzʊ polu klokɛnspili ɖɔɖɔ ɛzɩ ŋgandɩyɛ yɔ nɛ pamakɩ cɩm;cu ŋgʊ hɔɔlɩŋ ndɩ ndɩ taa. [[Fransɩɩ]] radio taa, ɖooo palkaɣ ndɔnjɔlɩyɛ naɖɩyɛ ɛlɛ, klokɛnspili ŋgandɩyɛ kɛ pahalaɣ pʊcɔ. Klokɛnspili cɩmʊ kʊnɛ kɛ cimɩŋ maɖaa sɔsaa nabayɩ kpaɣ nɛ palɩzɩna pe-wendu. Pa-taa kɔyɔ: Léo Ferré, Radiohead, [[Beatles]], Patrick Watson, [[Jimi Hendrix]] (Little Wing), Depeche Mode, Sagapool, Arcade Fire, Bumcello, Indochine nɛ Hanne Hukkelberg.

